00:42:24,200 --> 00:42:25,600
Because that girl...

546
00:42:34,800 --> 00:42:35,800
is...

547
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:41,360
I’m sorry. I have to take this call.

548
00:42:45,000 --> 00:42:46,280
Hello, what’s up?

549
00:42:47,000 --> 00:42:49,160
Come to the location I sent you
immediately.

550
00:42:51,400 --> 00:42:54,320
