552
00:42:56,880 --> 00:42:59,040
You must come quick.
Otherwise, you’re doomed.

553
00:42:59,360 --> 00:43:02,320
Hold on, it’s your job.
What does it have to do with me?

554
00:43:03,280 --> 00:43:04,840
In 15 minutes,

555
00:43:04,840 --> 00:43:06,560
if I don’t see you here,

556
00:43:06,560 --> 00:43:08,800
be prepared to answer your boss’ call.

557
00:43:09,320 --> 00:43:11,320
Hey, hold on.

558
00:43:15,760 --> 00:43:17,360
(Siam Amazing Park)

559
00:43:18,240 --> 00:43:20,040
An amusement park?

560
00:43:22,520 --> 00:43:27,080
I have to go now. It’s an urgent call.

561
00:43:28,320 --> 00:43:29,600
Right now?

562
00:43:30,560 --> 00:43:33,760
I’ll treat you to a meal later, alright?

563
00:43:34,240 --> 00:43:37,040
I’m sorry. See you later.

564
00:43:46,280 --> 00:43:47,920
What a Prapai thing to do.

565
00:43:58,820 --> 00:44:05,620
(Siam Amazing Park)

566
00:44:05,620 --> 00:44:07,880
I thought you said
you had a shooting going on.

567
00:44:11,920 --> 00:44:12,680
No.

568
00:44:14,120 --> 00:44:15,960
I just wanted to
come to an amusement park.

569
00:44:15,960 --> 00:44:17,880
But I don’t have any friends.

570
00:44:19,200 --> 00:44:22,160
What is wrong with you?
Why are you like this?

571
00:44:23,440 --> 00:44:26,280
I’m taking you out for some fun time.

572
00:44:26,280 --> 00:44:28,080
You should be happy.

573
00:44:28,560 --> 00:44:31,800
Unless I was interrupting you
with something.

574
00:44:33,720 --> 00:44:34,640
Were you on a date?

575
00:44:36,680 --> 00:44:37,720
No.

576
00:44:37,720 --> 00:44:38,520
Then good.

577
00:44:40,520 --> 00:44:42,400
You can go have fun alone.

578
00:44:42,400 --> 00:44:44,920
It’s my day off today. I’m out.

579
00:44:44,920 --> 00:44:46,600
Are you really going to go?

580
00:44:47,360 --> 00:44:49,880
I thought you said
you’d do everything I said.

581
00:44:52,720 --> 00:44:54,200
But I meant it being work-related.

582
00:44:54,200 --> 00:44:56,040
But I meant everything.

583
00:44:57,000 --> 00:44:59,120
Fine, if you want to go, you can.

584
00:45:00,640 --> 00:45:02,680
But I won’t promise

585
00:45:02,680 --> 00:45:05,160
if you’ll be seeing me
at the next shoot or not.

586
00:45:36,200 --> 00:45:40,280
(Special scene)

587
00:45:40,280 --> 00:45:41,880
Is this yours?

588
00:45:50,520 --> 00:45:54,080
Is this going to work? I’ll try.

589
00:45:57,920 --> 00:46:00,920
