591
00:46:09,000 --> 00:46:11,080
(Prapai likes colorful things)

592
00:46:12,520 --> 00:46:16,240
(Prapai likes furry things)

593
00:46:17,680 --> 00:46:23,280
(Prapai likes things
with lots of decorations)

594
00:46:29,680 --> 00:46:30,840
Open it.

595
00:46:34,920 --> 00:46:35,960
Do you like it?

